	<FactionDef ParentName="FactionBase">
		<defName>ViltrumEmpire</defName>
		<label>Empire of Viltrum</label>
		<categoryTag>Empire</categoryTag>
		<description>A ruthless, militaristic, expansionist, eugenic, ultratech empire. Their leaders and champions, the Viltrumites, are near-immortal superbeings.\n\nTheir advanced technology means they can greatly improve the lives of those who submit, but their sheer brutality and callousness makes resistance attractive to those with the power or will for it.\n\nViltrumites are a tiny portion of their population. Their underlings are equipped and enhanced with the empire's advanced technology, and so pose a serious threat with or without their masters present. They also utilize mechanoids.</description>
